instanceVariables.name: CurrentHP
instanceVariables.desc: Current hit point of the object implementing CombatInteractible.

instanceVariables.name: MaxHP
instanceVariables.desc: Default maximum hit point of the object implementing CombatInteractible.

instanceVariables.name: Immune
instanceVariables.desc: True when the object implementing CombatInteractible can't have its HP reduced. Immune expires when ImmuneRemainingTickCount reaches 0.

instanceVariables.name: ImmuneRemainingTickCount
instanceVariables.desc: Remaining tick count before the Immune boolean of the same object implementing CombatInteractible is set back to false.

instanceVariables.name: CurrentNegativeEffect
instanceVariables.desc: ID of the current negative effect affecting the object implementing CombatInteractible. The CurrentNegativeEffect is set back to -1 (No effect) when CurrentNegativeEffectRemainingTickCount reaches 0, or the effect is otherwise canceled.

instanceVariables.name: CurrentNegativeEffectRemainingTickCount
instanceVariables.desc: Remaining tick count before the CurrentNegativeEffect is set back to -1 (No effect).
